::Ramulus::

Ramulus jumps into a crouch as he sees Gekkidama tackle Brix, his eyes 
narrowing as he tries to aim his big gun into the struggle. Finally, the two 
bots stop moving around as much, Gekkidama obvioustly winning for now.

"No problem," Ramulus murmurs as three energy 'globs' leave his gun, heading 
at Gekkidama's shoulder (the one holding the launcher) at a high speed. In a 
direct hit, the shots would at least throw Gekkidama a dozen feet or so. 
Ramulus fires another shot, at the same target.
